WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:59.830 --> 02:00.910
(Legend has it)

02:01.270 --> 02:02.700
(that at the end of the East Sea)

02:03.110 --> 02:04.910
(stands the giant Fusang Tree.)

02:05.780 --> 02:07.030
(Beneath it)

02:07.390 --> 02:10.180
(lies the Void Spirit World.)

02:11.460 --> 02:13.460
(Unresolved mortal obsession)

02:13.700 --> 02:14.950
(gathers here.)

02:15.180 --> 02:16.860
(After centuries of cultivation,)

02:17.110 --> 02:19.140
(they become spirits.)

02:19.990 --> 02:21.740
(The one with the highest spirit power)

02:22.020 --> 02:23.670
(becomes the Sovereign of Spirits,)

02:24.070 --> 02:26.180
(ruling all spirits.)

02:27.270 --> 02:28.670
Welcome back,

02:28.670 --> 02:30.390
Your Grace.

02:31.220 --> 02:36.140
♪Forget the form to achieve♪

02:36.330 --> 02:40.060
♪Yet I can't♪

02:42.810 --> 02:48.090
♪Today, a home is granted♪

02:48.480 --> 02:52.760
♪Joy without grief♪

02:52.900 --> 02:54.580
(The current Sovereign)

02:54.990 --> 02:56.900
(was born a spirit.)

02:57.670 --> 02:58.950
(The greatest talent)

02:59.110 --> 03:01.350
(in ten generations.)

03:02.180 --> 03:05.940
(He Simu, Sovereign of Spirits)

03:06.830 --> 03:08.180
(The Sovereign)

03:08.420 --> 03:10.230
(loves roaming the mortal world,)

03:10.830 --> 03:12.020
(watching mortals)

03:12.270 --> 03:13.950
(experience joy and sorrow.)

03:15.140 --> 03:16.020
(Liangzhou)

03:16.580 --> 03:20.070
(is her chosen place to rest and watch.)

03:30.070 --> 03:31.790
(Though immortal,)

03:32.180 --> 03:34.580
(she was born blind to colors,)

03:34.950 --> 03:36.180
(numb to flavors,)

03:36.580 --> 03:38.070
(cold, and warmth.)

03:40.420 --> 03:43.070
(She lacks the five senses.)

03:46.670 --> 03:48.180
(Centuries ago,)

03:48.510 --> 03:50.740
(a Starhaven sorcerer said)

03:51.510 --> 03:55.230
(the master of the Deliverance Sword)

03:56.420 --> 03:58.900
(may be the spell bearer and bring her)

03:59.460 --> 04:00.460
(the five senses.)

04:03.830 --> 04:05.700
(But to this day,)

04:05.950 --> 04:08.670
(words of the past have long faded.)

04:09.580 --> 04:11.390
(Even the Sovereign herself)

04:11.860 --> 04:13.700
(has almost forgotten.)

04:39.140 --> 04:46.260
=Love Beyond the Grave=
=Episode 1=

05:08.820 --> 05:11.030
Save my son.

05:11.910 --> 05:14.620
Save Chenying.

05:22.910 --> 05:23.940
You're begging me?

05:25.990 --> 05:27.230
Aren't you afraid?

05:34.910 --> 05:35.750
Please.

05:35.820 --> 05:36.820
Save my son.

05:37.230 --> 05:38.350
Save my son.

05:38.350 --> 05:39.820
Please save my son.

05:41.030 --> 05:43.380
You are fatally wounded,

05:43.790 --> 05:44.790
but I can grant you

05:44.790 --> 05:46.180
one wish.

05:47.110 --> 05:48.420
By my rules,

05:49.300 --> 05:51.030
I will extract your obsession

05:51.620 --> 05:53.160
and save your son.

05:54.150 --> 05:55.350
Are you willing to let me?

05:58.550 --> 06:00.030
Anything to save my son.

06:01.060 --> 06:02.030
I accept.

06:04.990 --> 06:05.990
Deal.

06:36.710 --> 06:38.670
Such a deep obsession

06:39.620 --> 06:41.230
with his son.

06:42.910 --> 06:44.860
Mortals are so hard to understand.

06:57.350 --> 06:58.430
(Without a sense of touch,)

06:58.550 --> 06:59.550
(I struck too hard.)

07:10.700 --> 07:14.220
(Xue Chenying, Liangzhou villager)

07:24.060 --> 07:26.590
The Great Liang Army is here!

07:33.780 --> 07:35.700
(Liangzhou)

07:37.820 --> 07:39.710
People of Liangzhou, do not panic!

07:40.260 --> 07:41.150
The enemy is defeated!

07:41.910 --> 07:42.930
We, the Great Liang Army,

07:43.260 --> 07:44.590
will take over this city.

07:48.980 --> 07:52.260
(Duan Xu, Commander of Tabai Army)

07:52.260 --> 07:53.590
It's the Great Liang Army!

07:54.300 --> 07:56.500
- You're finally here!
- Great Liang's army!

07:57.590 --> 07:58.896
We'll do our utmost to protect

07:58.907 --> 07:59.990
all citizens in this city.

08:00.420 --> 08:01.880
- No need to hide anymore!
- Indeed!

08:02.110 --> 08:03.820
No need to hide anymore.

08:04.070 --> 08:05.220
The Great Liang Army.

08:05.550 --> 08:07.740
They're here to save us.

08:07.740 --> 08:09.730
They're finally here.

08:15.620 --> 08:16.590
(The Deliverance Sword.)

08:17.590 --> 08:19.380
(My aunt's spirit sword
from 300 years ago.)

08:19.595 --> 08:20.641
(Liang)
(Why would it be)

08:20.652 --> 08:21.985
(in the hands of a young general?)

08:34.260 --> 08:35.100
General.

08:37.740 --> 08:38.600
General.

08:38.620 --> 08:40.540
North Chong massacred the city
before leaving.

08:41.070 --> 08:42.900
Are you here to save us?

08:52.900 --> 08:55.140
Thank you, General.

08:56.260 --> 08:57.380
Thank you, General!

08:57.780 --> 08:58.780
Thank you, General.

09:04.020 --> 09:04.860
General,

09:05.110 --> 09:06.380
thank goodness you're here.

09:08.660 --> 09:09.500
Miss,

09:11.190 --> 09:12.110
wipe off the blood.

09:22.830 --> 09:24.350
(He really is just a mortal.)

09:44.230 --> 09:45.540
(This body is so weak.)

09:50.070 --> 09:50.910
Please help me.

09:51.590 --> 09:52.900
Save that child.

10:10.430 --> 10:11.270
Take her away.

10:11.500 --> 10:12.340
Take care of her.

10:17.020 --> 10:17.860
Pass down the order.

10:18.190 --> 10:19.740
Reorganize the troops in the city today.

10:19.950 --> 10:21.076
Aside from defensive duties,

10:21.540 --> 10:22.740
everyone must stay in the city

10:23.303 --> 10:24.636
to rescue the surviving civilians.

10:25.470 --> 10:26.990
Anyone caught looting or stealing

10:27.590 --> 10:28.516
will face military law.

10:28.730 --> 10:29.570
- Yes!
- Yes!

10:29.590 --> 10:31.950
(The Deliverance hasn't chosen
a master for 300 years.)

10:32.780 --> 10:34.140
(Could you be its master?)

10:35.060 --> 10:38.940
(Liangzhou Government Office)

10:40.780 --> 10:42.146
Our attack on the North Chong Army

10:42.590 --> 10:44.020
caught them completely off guard.

10:44.710 --> 10:45.590
Out of resentment,

10:45.590 --> 10:47.269
they sacked the city
during their retreat.

10:47.896 --> 10:49.069
This was a man-made disaster.

10:50.860 --> 10:52.470
We were still too late.

10:54.350 --> 10:55.729
How many men did we lose this time?

10:56.310 --> 10:57.256
We lost more than half.

10:57.710 --> 10:59.110
Less than 4,000 men remain.

10:59.660 --> 11:00.500
Xu,

11:00.626 --> 11:01.910
(Xia Qingsheng)
you're new here.

11:01.921 --> 11:03.339
(Meng Wan)
The troops are unsteady.

11:03.350 --> 11:04.660
If the enemy attacks now,

11:05.230 --> 11:06.430
we could hardly hold them off.

11:07.350 --> 11:08.276
How is your rheumatism?

11:08.710 --> 11:09.623
Any discomfort lately?

11:11.350 --> 11:12.656
The weather has been fine lately.

11:13.380 --> 11:14.220
I feel no discomfort.

11:16.435 --> 11:17.392
(It seems sunny weather)

11:17.403 --> 11:18.780
(isn't your favorite.)

11:23.830 --> 11:25.740
(The young general has other plans.)

11:25.860 --> 11:27.340
Father, please don't go.

11:27.710 --> 11:28.560
Father!

11:28.620 --> 11:29.460
Father!

11:31.470 --> 11:32.980
Father, where are you?

11:33.310 --> 11:34.150
Father!

11:34.780 --> 11:35.620
Father!

11:36.260 --> 11:38.350
(This child is truly a handful.)

11:43.620 --> 11:44.740
How are the siblings doing?

11:45.260 --> 11:46.780
The physician said they're exhausted.

11:47.027 --> 11:48.840
They'll recover
after resting for a few days.

11:49.310 --> 11:50.150
Take care of them.

11:50.590 --> 11:51.430
Xu,

11:51.710 --> 11:52.745
don't you think that girl

11:52.756 --> 11:53.500
is very strange?

11:53.973 --> 11:55.219
She mustn't stay here for long.

11:58.740 --> 11:59.580
Father!

12:01.140 --> 12:01.980
Where are you?

12:02.380 --> 12:03.220
Father!

12:05.830 --> 12:07.070
Father! Father!

12:11.990 --> 12:12.950
Don't leave me behind!

12:14.540 --> 12:15.740
Father! Father!

12:18.830 --> 12:19.670
Father!

12:20.740 --> 12:21.580
Father!

12:22.710 --> 12:23.710
Don't leave me!

12:23.860 --> 12:24.700
Father!

12:26.310 --> 12:27.150
Father!

12:27.430 --> 12:28.430
Don't go, Father!

12:28.660 --> 12:29.500
Father!

12:30.310 --> 12:31.150
Father!

12:31.740 --> 12:32.830
Please don't leave me!

12:33.230 --> 12:34.780
Father! Father!

12:34.900 --> 12:36.140
Don't leave me, Father!

12:36.260 --> 12:37.100
Father!

12:37.950 --> 12:38.790
Father!

12:39.020 --> 12:39.913
Please don't leave me!

12:40.380 --> 12:41.660
Father! Father!

12:42.660 --> 12:43.990
Father! Father!

12:44.470 --> 12:45.540
Father, don't leave me!

12:45.710 --> 12:47.020
Father! Father!

12:47.380 --> 12:48.280
Please don't leave me!

12:48.620 --> 12:50.110
For centuries, you're the first

12:50.110 --> 12:51.310
to ever grab my hand.

12:52.990 --> 12:53.830
Father.

12:55.780 --> 12:56.620
Father.

13:04.540 --> 13:05.380
Fengyi.

13:23.830 --> 13:24.670
Fengyi.

13:29.953 --> 13:31.886
(Hejia Fengyi)
Long time no see, Great Ancestor.

13:32.503 --> 13:33.802
You called for me late at night.

13:33.900 --> 13:35.590
Is there finally a way I can serve you?

13:35.780 --> 13:36.900
Help me look into someone.

13:37.740 --> 13:38.646
Someone from the court.

13:39.310 --> 13:40.710
The one wielding the Deliverance.

13:43.860 --> 13:45.260
The Deliverance has reappeared.

13:45.950 --> 13:46.950
Who is its master?

13:49.470 --> 13:50.310
It's...

13:53.620 --> 14:00.770
♪Cross your legs for three years♪

14:03.190 --> 14:04.030
Hurry up.

14:05.480 --> 14:09.050
♪Tether horse and ape♪

14:09.140 --> 14:10.195
(I'm Duan Xu, Commander)

14:10.206 --> 14:11.470
(of Great Liang's Tabai Army.)

14:12.590 --> 14:14.443
(Enemies retreated
north of the Guanhe River.)

14:15.740 --> 14:17.430
(Today, Liangzhou
returns to Great Liang.)

14:18.260 --> 14:19.740
(The Tabai Army will help you)

14:19.740 --> 14:20.580
(repair the houses)

14:22.230 --> 14:23.470
(and rebuild your homes.)

14:25.680 --> 14:32.680
♪Cross your legs for three years♪

14:33.570 --> 14:40.180
♪Subdue dragon and tiger;
tether horse and ape♪

14:40.310 --> 14:41.150
Thank you.

14:41.950 --> 14:42.790
Thank you.

14:43.430 --> 14:44.310
Thank you, General.

14:45.480 --> 14:48.560
♪Breath soft as silk♪

14:50.380 --> 14:51.273
(As long as I'm here,)

14:52.900 --> 14:54.860
(I'll protect the people of this city.)

14:54.860 --> 14:57.020
(Liangzhou)

14:57.020 --> 14:58.260
(As long as I draw breath,)

15:00.020 --> 15:01.540
(I will keep Liangzhou)

15:02.950 --> 15:03.900
(safe day and night.)

15:09.540 --> 15:10.430
It's warmer, right?

15:18.220 --> 15:24.380
(Liangzhou)

15:50.310 --> 15:51.150
You're awake.

15:57.140 --> 15:57.980
Eat up.

15:58.860 --> 15:59.830
Thank you, Miss.

16:00.990 --> 16:03.020
My name is He Xiaoxiao.

16:04.660 --> 16:05.500
Right now,

16:06.110 --> 16:07.620
my brother and I are weak.

16:08.260 --> 16:09.780
We wish to stay for a few days.

16:10.430 --> 16:11.620
Could you please

16:11.860 --> 16:12.700
ask the General

16:12.860 --> 16:13.780
to make an exception?

16:15.500 --> 16:16.340
By the way,

16:17.950 --> 16:19.380
about the General who saved me,

16:20.260 --> 16:21.430
what is his name?

16:21.950 --> 16:23.050
Something is wrong with you.

16:23.190 --> 16:24.030
You...

16:26.140 --> 16:27.540
Hey, come eat!

16:33.830 --> 16:34.670
Eat slowly.

16:47.140 --> 16:48.140
You are quite scheming.

16:48.590 --> 16:49.990
North Chong's famous Suanxian buns.

16:49.990 --> 16:51.260
Only their people can eat them.

16:51.350 --> 16:52.590
No wonder my brother threw up.

16:53.820 --> 16:54.660
If you suspect

16:54.660 --> 16:55.540
my brother and me,

16:55.860 --> 16:56.830
just kill us.

16:58.380 --> 17:00.260
Since it's North Chong's food,

17:00.900 --> 17:02.470
why did you recognize them at once?

17:02.950 --> 17:04.300
You are definitely up to no good.

17:04.540 --> 17:05.910
Why did you approach the General?

17:06.260 --> 17:07.470
Were you sent by North Chong?

17:10.390 --> 17:11.430
Don't bully my sister!

17:11.780 --> 17:13.100
We are not from North Chong,

17:13.230 --> 17:14.300
nor are we spies.

17:17.100 --> 17:18.820
Why do you keep trying to scare us?

17:19.390 --> 17:20.430
Either show evidence

17:20.500 --> 17:21.540
to prove we are spies

17:21.910 --> 17:23.190
or just kill us right here.

17:27.870 --> 17:28.950
I don't care if you work

17:28.950 --> 17:30.063
for North Chong or Duke Pei.

17:30.300 --> 17:31.580
Whatever you are planning,

17:31.580 --> 17:32.870
you'd better give up soon.

17:33.300 --> 17:34.580
Even if it costs my life,

17:35.190 --> 17:36.040
I will never let you

17:36.060 --> 17:37.500
lay a finger on my senior brother.

17:39.470 --> 17:40.670
Hearing you say this,

17:41.990 --> 17:43.470
the General is quite pitiful.

17:43.780 --> 17:44.630
Stop pretending.

17:48.540 --> 17:49.430
We're very busy.

17:49.870 --> 17:50.710
I'll leave now.

17:51.150 --> 17:51.990
Tomorrow morning,

17:52.470 --> 17:53.390
you must leave.

18:03.060 --> 18:04.093
Keep a close eye on them.

18:05.300 --> 18:06.140
Yes.

18:14.540 --> 18:15.380
What is your name?

18:20.340 --> 18:21.180
Xue Chenying.

18:35.150 --> 18:36.780
Xiaoxiao, don't you like food?

18:39.060 --> 18:40.910
I neither like nor dislike it.

18:42.060 --> 18:43.500
Whatever goes into my mouth,

18:43.500 --> 18:44.390
it has no taste at all.

19:24.710 --> 19:25.550
Hurry up and leave.

19:27.260 --> 19:29.540
(Serene and Clear)

20:03.520 --> 20:05.650
Please take me with you.

20:08.150 --> 20:10.670
Please take me with you.

20:20.500 --> 20:21.340
Right here.

20:21.500 --> 20:22.340
Start digging.

20:38.160 --> 20:42.360
Please take me with you.

21:13.230 --> 21:14.250
What's your father's name?

21:15.300 --> 21:16.780
Xue Mutou.

21:18.190 --> 21:19.030
Which characters?

21:21.870 --> 21:22.870
I can't read.

21:38.670 --> 21:39.950
Your father is already buried.

21:39.950 --> 21:41.016
Why are you crying for him?

21:41.380 --> 21:42.820
He should be the one crying for you.

21:42.820 --> 21:43.660
(Whittling Wood)

21:43.660 --> 21:44.780
His life has come to an end.

21:44.780 --> 21:45.886
He has no more worldly ties,

21:46.540 --> 21:47.670
leaving you, a little kid,

21:47.670 --> 21:48.870
in this chaotic borderland

21:49.540 --> 21:50.990
to survive all alone.

21:52.020 --> 21:53.740
You're the pitiful one here.

22:16.540 --> 22:17.990
Try throwing a handful yourself.

22:56.710 --> 22:58.580
What is this?

23:04.430 --> 23:05.363
What are you looking at?

23:05.990 --> 23:06.936
It's just a magic trick.

23:08.100 --> 23:09.190
So, Xiaoxiao,

23:09.190 --> 23:10.390
you're a trick master.

23:36.150 --> 23:37.100
Honey.

23:38.470 --> 23:40.060
Let's meet in the next life.

23:40.060 --> 23:41.950
My son must be back.

24:05.340 --> 24:06.630
What an amazing trick.

24:08.950 --> 24:10.910
(The General delivered himself to me.)

24:21.710 --> 24:22.950
Give it back! Give it back!

24:22.950 --> 24:23.790
Let go!

24:26.430 --> 24:28.020
You rob even the dead.

24:28.183 --> 24:29.503
Aren't you afraid of retribution?

24:29.580 --> 24:30.430
Get lost!

24:35.580 --> 24:36.540
Under Tabai Army rules,

24:38.150 --> 24:39.950
for any identifiable corpse,

24:40.540 --> 24:41.560
the belongings on the body

24:41.740 --> 24:43.470
must be fully returned to the family.

24:47.870 --> 24:48.820
You have a death wish!

24:58.950 --> 25:00.340
- Are you okay?
- Kill him!

25:00.500 --> 25:01.340
Yes, sir!

25:03.990 --> 25:04.830
(Draw your sword.)

25:05.300 --> 25:06.190
(Hurry up.)

25:19.300 --> 25:20.190
- Let's go!
- Hurry!

25:20.740 --> 25:21.580
Let's go!

25:25.160 --> 25:26.020
Thank you.

25:26.020 --> 25:26.990
Thank you, sir.

25:29.910 --> 25:31.260
Lay your loved ones to rest.

25:31.820 --> 25:32.670
Thank you.

25:32.670 --> 25:33.630
Thank you, sir.

25:39.660 --> 25:41.260
(Whittling Wood)

25:42.870 --> 25:44.710
Rest in peace.

25:49.670 --> 25:50.510
General.

25:50.780 --> 25:51.620
General.

25:53.190 --> 25:54.030
General.

25:55.950 --> 25:57.390
General, you saved us yesterday.

25:57.863 --> 25:59.196
My brother and I can't repay you.

25:59.376 --> 26:00.382
Please accept our thanks.

26:04.740 --> 26:06.273
Miss, please stop calling me General.

26:06.740 --> 26:08.100
It's best not to alert the others.

26:10.540 --> 26:11.380
General,

26:11.870 --> 26:13.260
are you traveling incognito?

26:13.870 --> 26:15.100
You have a sharp eye, Miss.

26:16.100 --> 26:17.260
We only met briefly yesterday.

26:18.260 --> 26:19.690
Even with my veil on today,

26:20.390 --> 26:21.630
you recognized me instantly.

26:21.910 --> 26:22.750
Of course.

26:23.710 --> 26:25.020
You're highly renowned

26:25.540 --> 26:26.580
and look so heroic.

26:27.500 --> 26:28.340
I've admired you

26:30.060 --> 26:31.710
for so long.

26:33.260 --> 26:34.100
Is that so?

26:36.020 --> 26:37.150
Then what is my name?

26:48.430 --> 26:49.820
No need for flattery, Miss.

26:50.190 --> 26:51.540
If I were truly that renowned,

26:51.780 --> 26:52.820
I should've kept Liangzhou

26:52.820 --> 26:53.870
from being destroyed.

26:59.260 --> 27:00.100
My name is Duan Xu,

27:01.440 --> 27:02.830
as in a supreme martial achievement.

27:03.910 --> 27:05.003
My courtesy name is Shunxi.

27:13.950 --> 27:15.260
My name is He Xiaoxiao.

27:16.630 --> 27:17.670
This is my sworn brother.

27:17.950 --> 27:18.790
He's named Chenying.

27:20.060 --> 27:20.900
Miss He.

27:25.500 --> 27:26.340
Watch out.

27:52.500 --> 27:54.206
(The Deliverance chose him
as its master.)

27:55.470 --> 27:56.780
(Who exactly is he?)

27:58.150 --> 27:59.100
North Chong soldiers!

27:59.100 --> 28:00.060
Catch them!

28:00.430 --> 28:01.270
- Yes!
- Yes!

28:03.150 --> 28:04.740
You aren't the only one

28:06.280 --> 28:07.150
who recognized me.

28:07.150 --> 28:08.580
That was so scary!

28:13.780 --> 28:14.620
You're safe now.

28:15.580 --> 28:16.500
Thanks for your help.

28:18.230 --> 28:19.990
I wish I could say there's no need

28:20.150 --> 28:21.340
for thanks just like you,

28:23.190 --> 28:24.260
but my brother and I

28:24.780 --> 28:25.780
have no family left.

28:26.150 --> 28:27.596
Driven out of the Prefect's Mansion,

28:27.870 --> 28:29.670
we are now homeless,

28:29.670 --> 28:30.870
with no food or shelter.

28:31.820 --> 28:33.230
It's about to snow.

28:34.190 --> 28:35.220
We don't even know

28:35.231 --> 28:36.271
where we'll sleep tonight.

28:44.340 --> 28:45.180
Alright.

28:46.446 --> 28:47.646
I'll help you and your brother

28:47.657 --> 28:48.486
find a place to stay.

28:50.260 --> 28:51.100
Thank you, General.

28:55.630 --> 28:56.870
You just mentioned

28:58.780 --> 28:59.710
it will snow later?

29:01.060 --> 29:02.630
The weather is very odd this year.

29:03.190 --> 29:04.800
Even the Guanhe River has frozen over.

29:04.870 --> 29:06.020
Snowing on a sunny day

29:06.240 --> 29:07.470
isn't that strange anymore.

29:08.100 --> 29:09.470
Though the sun is bright now,

29:09.990 --> 29:11.430
the weather will change soon.

29:12.260 --> 29:14.390
My eyes are very sharp.

29:17.150 --> 29:17.990
Come with me.

29:26.910 --> 29:28.430
(He has no spiritual arts,)

29:28.630 --> 29:30.710
(yet the Deliverance chose him.)

29:31.500 --> 29:32.990
(How is he worthy)

29:32.990 --> 29:35.300
(of the Deliverance?)

29:37.990 --> 29:38.830
Xiaoxiao,

29:39.500 --> 29:40.470
it's snowing.

29:46.230 --> 29:47.300
It really is snowing.

29:50.540 --> 29:52.040
Miss, you were exactly right.

30:04.260 --> 30:05.670
You were out for a day and a night.

30:06.100 --> 30:06.910
If you catch a cold,

30:06.921 --> 30:08.227
I don't want to take care of you.

30:41.790 --> 30:45.490
♪Falling down like snow♪

30:45.980 --> 30:49.530
♪Joys and sorrows of the mortal world♪

30:49.530 --> 30:53.230
♪Swept along by the daylight♪

30:53.760 --> 30:57.410
♪The forms and hues of the mortal realm♪

30:57.820 --> 31:00.480
♪Lingering for a fleeting moment♪

31:00.740 --> 31:02.150
You were unconscious for a day too.

31:03.100 --> 31:03.940
Don't catch a cold.

31:06.540 --> 31:08.106
Don't miss the beauty of the first snow.

31:09.670 --> 31:10.990
Let's walk back together.

31:16.330 --> 31:19.930
♪Dawn and dusk rise and set♪

31:20.100 --> 31:23.810
♪Longing to meet, yet parted by destiny♪

31:24.110 --> 31:27.830
♪Let me wander through♪

31:27.830 --> 31:31.450
♪Light and dark, without turning back♪

31:32.840 --> 31:33.710
(Mortals can be moved)

31:33.710 --> 31:35.190
(by such petty sights.)

31:35.430 --> 31:38.970
♪Accompanied by the abyss♪

31:38.990 --> 31:39.830
(What a pity.)

31:41.100 --> 31:42.600
(I am blind to colors, deaf to music,)

31:43.580 --> 31:45.100
(and numb to cold, warmth, and taste.)

31:46.500 --> 31:47.780
(All beings are like dust,)

31:49.137 --> 31:50.510
(living and dying in a single day.)

31:50.700 --> 31:51.980
(Tianshuo)

31:51.990 --> 31:53.150
(No matter how many)

31:53.150 --> 31:54.580
(deep and fervent desires they hold,)

31:55.990 --> 31:57.630
(they're all but an illusion.)

31:59.740 --> 32:01.460
Great Liang once had a vast territory.

32:01.460 --> 32:02.180
(Great Liang)

32:02.191 --> 32:04.169
Now, it borders North Chong
at the Guanhe River.

32:04.180 --> 32:04.836
(North Chong)

32:04.847 --> 32:05.987
The North and South face off.

32:06.960 --> 32:07.910
North Chong has occupied

32:07.910 --> 32:10.256
the 17 Prefectures north
of the Guanhe River for 60 years.

32:11.570 --> 32:13.390
A winter like this comes once
in a century.

32:14.763 --> 32:16.076
The Guanhe River has frozen over.

32:16.570 --> 32:18.230
The North Chong Army crossed,

32:18.450 --> 32:19.820
pillaging Yuzhou and Liangzhou.

32:21.563 --> 32:22.814
Though we used a surprise attack

32:22.825 --> 32:23.619
to retake Liangzhou,

32:23.630 --> 32:24.910
the North Chong Army

32:25.340 --> 32:26.920
is still lurking outside the city.

32:27.630 --> 32:29.000
The Tabai Army inside the city

32:29.470 --> 32:30.830
is forced into a besieged defense.

32:31.300 --> 32:32.310
The situation is dire.

32:34.870 --> 32:36.020
Duan Shunxi?

32:36.260 --> 32:37.580
Everyone

32:37.580 --> 32:38.780
in the court

32:38.780 --> 32:39.670
knows him.

32:40.340 --> 32:42.230
His family is renowned for scholars

32:42.230 --> 32:43.520
and imperial relations.

32:43.540 --> 32:45.550
Two years ago, he became
the Second-Place Scholar

32:45.561 --> 32:46.465
and became an official,

32:46.476 --> 32:48.540
highly valued by Chancellor Du,

32:48.540 --> 32:50.630
groomed as a future Chief Councilor.

32:51.190 --> 32:52.830
Born to a civil official clan,

32:53.580 --> 32:55.430
why did he take charge
of this border post?

33:00.190 --> 33:01.870
Duan Xu...

33:02.670 --> 33:03.870
He has a sworn foe at court,

33:04.430 --> 33:05.820
the Top Scholar of his exam year,

33:06.190 --> 33:09.020
Fang Xianye, Censorial Counselor.

33:12.710 --> 33:14.260
Duan Xu was impeached by him

33:14.260 --> 33:15.340
and ended up in the army.

33:15.870 --> 33:18.150
Fang Xianye is sharp

33:18.300 --> 33:19.430
and careful in every move,

33:19.430 --> 33:21.020
always outshining Duan Shunxi.

33:23.630 --> 33:24.630
Duan Shunxi fell

33:25.230 --> 33:26.950
from a Chief Councilor candidate

33:26.950 --> 33:28.710
to a general post that may not last.

33:29.500 --> 33:30.870
The one you call

33:31.100 --> 33:32.910
known to all, far and wide,

33:33.770 --> 33:35.990
is that famed unlucky soul.

33:42.950 --> 33:43.790
Who is it?

33:46.950 --> 33:47.790
No one.

33:47.990 --> 33:48.830
Let's go.

33:49.150 --> 33:49.990
Go.

33:49.990 --> 33:51.430
Great Ancestor, Duan Xu...

33:51.430 --> 33:52.670
The Deliverance chose

33:52.910 --> 33:54.430
a dying man.

33:54.870 --> 33:55.740
What do you mean?

33:56.630 --> 33:57.910
In these chaotic times,

33:58.580 --> 33:59.740
he's surrounded by enemies.

34:00.100 --> 34:01.470
How long can he last?

34:03.430 --> 34:04.390
According to my rules,

34:04.390 --> 34:05.540
I'll ask him what his wish is

34:06.260 --> 34:07.340
and grant it.

34:08.270 --> 34:09.220
After he dies,

34:09.220 --> 34:10.350
I'll take the Deliverance.

34:10.620 --> 34:12.020
We won't be taking it for nothing.

34:31.990 --> 34:32.990
It's been 300 years.

34:34.310 --> 34:36.100
The Deliverance finally has a master.

34:36.430 --> 34:38.100
I actually lived to see this day.

34:40.700 --> 34:41.540
No.

34:43.310 --> 34:44.390
(My ancestor is Ji Xi.)

34:44.540 --> 34:45.846
(She's the Great Ancestor's aunt)

34:46.180 --> 34:48.020
(and the best Starhaven sorcerer.)

34:48.500 --> 34:50.140
(She once mentioned in her notes)

34:50.580 --> 34:52.100
(that mortals who bear the spell)

34:52.100 --> 34:53.540
(are extremely rare.)

34:54.060 --> 34:55.622
(Could the master of the Deliverance)

34:55.633 --> 34:57.430
(that appeared after 300 years)

34:57.750 --> 34:59.910
(be the Great Ancestor's spell bearer?)

35:00.830 --> 35:03.310
(Then she can get her five senses.)

35:16.260 --> 35:17.140
Assassins!

35:17.140 --> 35:17.980
Watch out, General!

35:20.920 --> 35:21.790
Guards!

35:21.790 --> 35:22.630
Protect the General!

35:37.910 --> 35:39.310
(This body is freezing to death.)

35:39.990 --> 35:41.470
(How delicate.)

35:42.540 --> 35:44.270
(If not to nourish this body,)

35:44.870 --> 35:46.196
(I wouldn't bother bringing her.)

35:51.750 --> 35:52.590
Xiaoxiao!

35:52.870 --> 35:54.070
Don't leave me!

35:57.180 --> 35:58.020
Xiaoxiao!

36:00.350 --> 36:01.190
Xiaoxiao.

36:03.470 --> 36:04.430
Xiaoxiao.

36:05.220 --> 36:06.060
Xiaoxiao.

36:06.700 --> 36:07.990
Xiaoxiao, where are you?

36:09.020 --> 36:09.860
Xiaoxiao.

36:22.220 --> 36:23.220
My child.

36:26.140 --> 36:27.100
My child.

36:33.390 --> 36:34.700
My child.

36:36.500 --> 36:37.540
Don't be afraid.

36:39.430 --> 36:41.180
Come to Mother.

36:42.790 --> 36:44.590
Stay away!

37:03.950 --> 37:05.310
- Chase! Capture them!
- Chase!

37:05.310 --> 37:06.150
- Yes!
- Yes!

37:52.540 --> 37:54.100
(My Spirits Lantern)

37:54.910 --> 37:56.880
(actually fears the Deliverance?)

38:01.660 --> 38:03.220
(Let me see)

38:03.620 --> 38:06.580
(why the Deliverance
chose you as its master.)

38:20.160 --> 38:25.490
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

38:25.820 --> 38:30.070
♪Light encountered shadow♪

38:31.430 --> 38:36.800
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

38:37.100 --> 38:41.700
♪The unbreakable fate♪

38:42.790 --> 38:44.630
♪Suddenly cracked♪

38:56.840 --> 39:02.280
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

39:02.460 --> 39:06.790
♪Light encountered shadow♪

39:08.160 --> 39:13.550
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

39:13.780 --> 39:17.720
♪The unbreakable fate♪

39:19.490 --> 39:21.380
♪Suddenly cracked♪

39:24.040 --> 39:27.200
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

39:27.200 --> 39:29.730
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

39:29.730 --> 39:35.250
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

39:35.250 --> 39:38.490
♪Following fate's guidance♪

39:38.490 --> 39:43.350
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

39:43.690 --> 39:46.710
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

39:46.710 --> 39:49.530
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

39:49.790 --> 39:52.320
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

39:52.320 --> 39:57.740
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

39:57.910 --> 40:00.980
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

40:01.140 --> 40:06.040
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

40:06.250 --> 40:09.720
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
